      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the helplines. i've seen them. but they don't get it. they just say \"it gets better\" like it's some magic trick. it doesn't feel like it's going to get better. it feels like i'm just waiting for a pain that never stops. i feel like a ghost in my own house.",
